(asociado a embarazo)","guid":"XCUF7Dj-2GMMa2lHLIOs9Q","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Pico 2: Edad avanzada (mediana ~75 años),\\Nasociado a autoinmunidad/malignidad","guid":"EyaLP8O1GR_RTyCNfWivTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"12","text":"◊ Afecta ambos sexos","guid":"asYyCH05WgO0GzDuecomgg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"12","text":"◊ Ligera predominancia masculina (~1.2:1)","guid":"m6lFJlIgnFZoqPTBEtqC7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"4","text":"› Factores de Riesgo y\\NCondiciones Predisponentes","guid":"Yi0pmKD15_W1C0EgoVba8Q","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"◊ Idiopática: ~50-80% casos","guid":"4KeCxaR8frXQE5JuauiILQ","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"◊ Trastornos Autoinmunes:\\N~10% casos","guid":"VgHHfxVQsTNnp-2kQi4iBA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Ejemplos: Artritis Reumatoide, LES, Enf. Tiroidea Autoinmune","guid":"rcUQMuwoy9EB6527g4E95g","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• ★ Factor riesgo significativo: Enf. Alzheimer comórbida","guid":"X8qi3Bz71FkfapG8BT9VnQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• ⇄ Relación con envejecimiento inmune (Inmunosenescencia, Inflammaging ★):\\NAlteración células T, ↓regulación inmune, disbiosis","guid":"9GgPv9ldsiu_L5lpbxy67Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"19","text":"◊ Neoplasias Malignas:\\N~10% casos","guid":"ybTFeI_j98DYEou7lvMpaw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Tipos: Hematológicas (linfoproliferativas), Tumores sólidos (próstata, pulmón, GI)","guid":"msB7685CI90sX3x0FNlYGg","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Posible rol: Microambiente tumoral, Rsp. inmune aberrante","guid":"JQtPa1FVZTYi8RIaUh-hJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"19","text":"◊ Embarazo y Postparto:\\N2-15% casos","guid":"levq_t4Vah4zsdFXzyP6oA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Mecanismo: No claro,\\Ncambios inmunes maternos","guid":"YSDrNIJNkheOjiu8GBSv1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"19","text":"◊ Medicamentos:\\N3-5% casos","guid":"IWWPoJ6Og-1Q-IfccW51Ww","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Ejemplos: Penicilinas, Cefalosporinas, Interferones, Clopidogrel,\\NAlemtuzumab, Omalizumab (**Konstantinov K. et al., 2023**)","guid":"DzYfXnfh0tzCJvvQU3DFEg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Inicio: Mediana edad 75 años, mediana tiempo 30 días","guid":"eiSwzvTJ4YZgn9K7ieqqqQ","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"• Mortalidad asociada: 10%","guid":"0uBbW5SY9Xy7Gv4ZNI-sWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"19","text":"◊ Vacunación Anti-SARS-CoV-2: Reportes (19 casos, revisión sistemática), mayoría\\Nhombres mayores, comórbidos, vacunas ARNm. Causalidad no probada ★.","guid":"M3iS72W64PAk0B8fcefbhw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"- Patogénesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"› Naturaleza\\NAutoinmune ★","guid":"yEt9ocmx9PG7ayI_aClplA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"◊ Reconocimiento erróneo FVIII → Rsp. inmune","guid":"83Z1tcept0tvzbhPd-rQRQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"◊ Producción anticuerpos inhibidores → Neutralización + ↑Aclaramiento FVIII","guid":"G4yO-zZP7hXHr9p2dVGcJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"› Mecanismos Propuestos","guid":"h8MaCLp_0kW0XX3mgVLzpw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"◊ Ruptura tolerancia inmune a FVIII","guid":"C4hUA4Ek8iqoW5dbabpqkg","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"› Anticuerpos Inhibidores\\N(Autoanticuerpos) ★","guid":"mqKpwmO-XgOeiXArdNzL7Q","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"◊ Dianas principales: Dominios\\NFVIII **A2**, **A3**, **C2**","guid":"srvC3hQIibkVKFt_uG1ZEw","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Función dominios: A2/A3 (interacción FIXa/FX), C2 (unión fosfolípidos/vWF)","guid":"bR0F37T9wPL8kZcpm6gu1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"◊ Características: IgG\\Npoliclonal (IgG1, IgG4) ★","guid":"83oldnaWgUuQsaDXLIs6aw","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• ⇄ Similitud con Aloanticuerpos (Hemofilia Congénita):\\NIgG1/IgG4, mismas dianas","guid":"pR5hGA77i3058dZnbKFShA","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"41","text":"◊ ⇄ Diferencia vs Aloanticuerpos:\\NCinética inactivación ★","guid":"6KESYWXF_SnQ8iWPeItekg","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Aloanticuerpos (Congénita): Mayoría \"tipo 1\" (lineal, completa)","guid":"_cKjgQPxVeIA3yueTVZe8w","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• Autoanticuerpos (HAA): Mayoría \"tipo 2\" (compleja, no lineal, dependiente T°/tiempo, 2º orden) ★","guid":"kolHIV1PSEEhF9fU_QyiMw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"• Implicación Tipo 2: FVIII residual no protector, posible subestimación potencia inhibidor","guid":"na5KWFrpepSTqE4-LJVudQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"35","text":"› Impacto Clínico","guid":"f4dsVZVfZJlYC5jZ5cR2xw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"◊ Dificulta terapia reemplazo FVIII","guid":"Mn_SlbfDz98IxFspGEJk4g","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"◊ Dificulta control hemostático","guid":"pCvV0gbNlRRb8kDO1QL-Mg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"0","text":"- Clínica y\\NDiagnóstico","guid":"M_Kc5B3fW1677GIjHxt1BA","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"› Presentación\\NClínica","guid":"2lD0z5C_uPDRe04EJqt_wQ","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"◊ Variable","guid":"IIhbzv643WLGJxnhEhFC3w","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"◊ Reto: Falta conciencia → Retraso diagnóstico/tto (★ **EACH2**: 34% retraso ≥1 sem)","guid":"TCKpAQVBPpXzXkq9UB4JHA","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"◊ Síntomas: Sangrado espontáneo/prolongado (tejidos blandos, piel, músculo, mucosas), hematomas, sangrado post-trauma/cirugía","guid":"3m2QbRV9PXQg_yJudqXJtw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"◊ Severidad: Hemorragias GI/intracraneales (riesgo vital)","guid":"SHHzSzamO9eKweQygLePsw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"◊ Asintomáticos: ~10% (investigar TTPa prolongado pre-invasivo)","guid":"HO9tET2eE02n_PveSNbFow","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"54","text":"◊ Patrón sangrado vs Congénita: Infrecuente hemartrosis, frecuente tejidos blandos, muscular, mucoso, GI, GU, HIC","guid":"hjtnkKZ6kZo6U5Kqcrn4zQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"53","text":"› Hallazgos Laboratorio y\\NEvaluación Hemostática","guid":"lsT8fkv4hhemmNiHrJmhaA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"◊ Clave: Prolongación aislada TTPa ★","guid":"tNTwTE4ZhZkppDKcKHw3WQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"◊ Estudios Mezcla: TTPa no corrige (plasma paciente + normal 1:1), esp. tras incubación 2h 37°C ★","guid":"qadfELHpBCo6Drz-gErAwA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"◊ Actividad FVIII: Muy reducida (<0.3 IU/dL, a menudo <0.01 IU/dL)","guid":"zah76WTraBA4DxgTUlhJmw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"◊ Otros factores (FIX, FXI, FXII, vWF): Normales","guid":"yuWwUgF6fXOTRD8r_1B_EQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"◊ Ensayo Bethesda (modificación Nijmegen ★): Cuantifica inhibidor (BU/mL)","guid":"sqMOXsaoy74m62Mf0nighw","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Limitación: Cinética tipo 2 puede subestimar","guid":"hGuOAXWs9aY8B9dv90l3bw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"53","text":"› Diagnóstico\\NDiferencial","guid":"b0icWe1dDCSHA2yR_6JzvQ","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"◊ Hemofilia Congénita A","guid":"6LK8bqPgxW8FrmF7kdPlFw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"◊ Enfermedad von Willebrand (EvW)","guid":"oDOw3kBwJ--5oePByAlYkQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"◊ Síndrome von Willebrand Adquirido (SvWA) ★","guid":"-qfIqGs3Rz5pJPy7TVJtXg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"◊ Inhibidores adquiridos otros factores (raros)","guid":"3bTMh5tVFN-49L8ifXiVwQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"◊ Otras Coagulopatías Adquiridas (Enf. hepática, CID, Déficit Vit K)","guid":"bXa-uY3tvH7oakpF7s-25g","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"68","text":"◊ Trastornos Plaquetarios (PTI, defectos función)","guid":"drwkmFV448_FF2YuuAfTHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"0","text":"- Tratamiento\\Ny Manejo","guid":"M7g5vALOVZZll4ZTAsZ9hQ","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"› Objetivos\\NPrimarios ★","guid":"1uK2u6HwGgx_w0Ql7sMODA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"◊ Controlar sangrado agudo","guid":"sdTdYozMzO7Gm2hMTNEFaw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"◊ Erradicar inhibidores (restaurar hemostasia)","guid":"JcTJD6qso-hHxjUKGNG3RA","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"› Enfoque Multidisciplinario","guid":"hecbRCit9U_WNBwIwH7mlw","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"75","text":"› Control Hemostático y\\NManejo Sangrado","guid":"ORuOeGNEH1YAWy_34uLwFg","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"◊ Terapia Reemplazo FVIII: Generalmente ineficaz","guid":"bjrjrm0ehv8GyTBWHjub4w","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"◊ FVIII Porcino Recombinante (rpFVIII): Opción","guid":"Ev7pE2gKbAhuMEE90nSYcQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"◊ Medidas Locales: Compresión, sutura, etc.","guid":"_Gy3OYvtZMXgu83DbJK_Dw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"◊ Agentes de\\NBypass ★","guid":"6fuDWCtG9Q-mkL-rspJUJg","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Clásicos: aPCC (FEIBA), rFVIIa","guid":"yg9T8Y0sRp3B5n0r9CovJg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"• Nuevo Agente: **Emicizumab** ★ (Ac. biespecífico mimetiza FVIII)","guid":"LFwhwkbBCViDP3Ueyszt5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"80","text":"◊ Uso actual: Profilaxis (off-label), Coadyuvante sangrado agudo. Estudios (**AGEHA**)","guid":"sgV4eVwnLLokwTzX9vrHFg","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"80","text":"◊ Ventajas: Subcutáneo, dosificación espaciada","guid":"a1yvu2s6y0--zwgm8zJ61Q","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"80","text":"◊ Riesgos: Trombosis, monitorizar FVIII (>50% → suspender)","guid":"QXsCM91TTRFj